# Enterprise Scale Assumptions

The platform must support environments containing:

* Large numbers of COBOL programs
* Large numbers of JCL artifacts
* Large numbers of Copybooks
* Large numbers of DB2 objects
* Large numbers of CICS transactions
* Large numbers of scheduler definitions

The architecture should assume enterprise-scale repositories rather than project-scale repositories.

